{"tid":1982410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當着防暴警自瀆　越南漢獲判罰款了事","createTime":"2020-04-21T07:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T13:49:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":379,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfbf53cc5e1f3ee8a5211624bb8d12586628274","tid":1982410,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"去年10月31日大批市民聚集旺角街頭，警方於彌敦道設立防線應對，惟一名醉酒越南中年漢竟走到防線前，拉開褲鍊當着警員面前套弄陽具。該越南男子今日（21日）在西九龍法院承認在公眾地方作出猥褻行為罪，求情指因母親離世情緒大受影響，事發前飲了6罐啤酒消愁，受酒精響下才會犯案。裁判官考慮到被告認罪，判處他罰款2000港元。<br />\n<br />\n50歲越南籍被告趙文俊，持香港身份證，報稱是臨時清潔工。案情指，去年10月31日有人在旺角彌敦道與鴉蘭街交界聚集，至晚上10時許，被告穿過集結人群走到警方防線前約3米位置，並拉下牛仔褲的褲鏈。警員見狀試圖喝止，惟被告充耳不聞，更取出陽具，用右手緊握前後移動7至8下。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 方向報"},{"pid":"91bf4a6e60c3ebdb1b1e61470b4c18980bc75faf","tid":1982410,"uid":107577,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:54:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線需要你<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong_promo_int @guardiansofhongkong<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=bed851bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n做任務，推任務，整圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cm4FxNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCm4FxNr.jpg&h=15d08911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJWHL7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJWHL7v.jpg&h=a12ee600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZ7ovza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZ7ovza.jpg&h=9d247f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E8iabu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E8iabu.jpg&h=b31746d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f8a4755b1a97e7a25cd54db05c4e9960b8fe655","tid":1982410,"uid":68158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e736d770f10acfa8170a876287bbad1b3ff6522e","tid":1982410,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86af6f82d1fce0a5dfc04a34b9a4ecc2033252a9","tid":1982410,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb29c25868d7c3debe9a74fd1d4a886768865b5","tid":1982410,"uid":77196,"like":284,"dislike":2,"score":282,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"真係撚狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0e7101f393593ea8a2d7cae22c0404244a00d7","tid":1982410,"uid":12704,"like":189,"dislike":2,"score":187,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"J防暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n射精襲警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694db1396b523c4bceb2e85349a6272b0cbfa6e5","tid":1982410,"uid":19552,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"LIVE新聞冇印象既"},{"pid":"64f2f6c3fae9ea66970018a24b91b9b2b1dd867f","tid":1982410,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好厲害"},{"pid":"227a0eb9a7c1a7d55e0cf9076a235787d0364f3b","tid":1982410,"uid":134683,"like":133,"dislike":2,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"老母死左同當衆打飛機都可以拉埋嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm